QuestData.Title: Proof of Strength: Goren Tooth
QuestData.Description: This tooth is proof of your strength at slaying goren and your gladiator friend has born witness!$b$bTake the tooth back to Limbflayer and claim your accolades!
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the proof to Limbflayer at Beastwatch in Gorgrond.
QuestData.RewardText: We are impressed with your ability to slay the goren. They are relentless and voracious and can overwhelm those are not prepared.
